  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "The documentation page @BryanSchuetz links to, does not clearly explain how to implement this with the `instantsearch.js` library. Nor does the `SearchParameter` section on the algoliasearch-helper-js [reference page](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html#searchparameters).\r\n\r\nI've got it working with the following code:\r\n```javascript\r\nconst search = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: '',\r\n  apiKey: '',\r\n  indexName: '',\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    facetingAfterDistinct: true,\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2018-01-05T09:47:02Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/684#issuecomment-355513805",
    "id": 355513805,
    "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/algolia/instantsearch/issues/684",
