    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "In case this can help someone coming across this issue like I did, here's how to provide custom search parameters in React instantSearch in order to fix the incorrect facet counts in the refinement list:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<InstantSearch \r\n  // ...\r\n>\r\n\r\n  <Configure distinct={1} facetingAfterDistinct={true} />\r\n\r\n</InstantSearch>\r\n```",
